# Web3Forms access key for the Contact page form.
#
# 1. Get a free key at https://web3forms.com (enter your email → Create Access Key).
# 2. Copy this file to .env.local and paste your real key below (git-ignored).
# 3. For production, also add VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY in your Vercel project:
#    Settings → Environment Variables → add for Production, then redeploy
#    (VITE_* vars are baked in at build time, so a rebuild is required).
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
